Woodland.Yolo, California: Yolo (formerly Cacheville, Cochran's Crossing, Cochranes Crossing, Hutton's Ranch, and Travelers Home) is an unincorporated community and census-designated place in Yolo County, California. It is located 4.9 miles northwest of the county seat, Woodland. Yolo's ZIP Code is 95697 and its area code 530.
